[DhtmlXQ_comment1_31]And red has the advantage!||All of red's chess pieces are well developed and applying much pressure on black. 　[/DhtmlXQ_comment1_31]
[DhtmlXQ_comment2_30]And both sides would be in attack mode. ||Black can be satisfied with this outcome.[/DhtmlXQ_comment2_30]
